==Описание==

The {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_StyleBold.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_StyleBold|Spreadsheet StyleBold]]}} tool makes the text inside the cell adopt '''bold''' style.

==Применение==

# Make sure there is an active {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet]]}} open so that the button is enabled.
# Select a cell.
# Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_StyleBold.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_StyleBold|Spreadsheet StyleBold]]}} button.


